0in 0in 12pt">&nbsp;</DIV>\r\n<DIV style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt">11/2004 – Now</SPAN></DIV>\r\n<DIV style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt"><STRONG><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black">Scitec Co.,Ltd - HCM</SPAN></STRONG><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt"><BR>Software Programmer<BR>I work for Scitec Co. as Software Programmer.<BR>My company has a lot of Project, but I''m join in the team with project "AnGiang".<BR>In these first times, my team has 4 person. What''s my position ? With small group, we find the way to develop this project.<BR>And then, I become one of leader of my small group for coding project (this project has various part).<BR>We use VB.NET for project.<BR>Database : MS SQL 2000<BR>Report : Crystal Report 9.0<BR>Component : C1FlexGrid<BR>Type : 3 tier<BR>And now, My former colleague and I write class for my company</SPAN>.<BR><BR></DIV>\r\n<DIV style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 12pt"><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 10pt; COLOR: black">02/2004 - 10/2004<BR><STRONG>Visionex Software Development Company Ltd. - Ho Chi Minh</STRONG><BR>Software Programmer<BR>Language : VB 6<BR>Database : MS SQL 2000<BR>Report : Crystal 8.5<BR>I''m join in company, and write some project with myself.<BR>Yes, sometime just with myself. Because this company''s small. And maybe I hired for some projects.<BR>I begin with project "VIA software". This program wirte for the Insurance Company. It assist employeee manage clients, accidents, and a lot of information about insurance.<BR>I left company when the projects finished, and my company closed. But from that, I have a lot of experience about insurance, coding, and working.<BR><BR>10/2003 - 02/2004<BR><STRONG>CB Richard Ellis (Vietnam) Co., Ltd - HCM</STRONG><BR>Part-time Staff<BR>CBRE is the "International Property Consultants" company. I''m work as part-time staff.<BR>Like the students - my friends, the student life''s always ebullient. I always get the part-time job when I have the free time, or when I need it. And one of my